author: Fiachra Ó Cionnaith
title: Irish citizens stuck on cruise during Covid-19 outbreak
description: Up to a dozen Irish citizens are on board a cruise liner which is being refused entry to Panama after four passengers died from coronavirus and more than 140 others contracted the virus.
content:
